    Information

    All-in-one culture diversity platform for HKUST students

    About Us

    We are a group of students from the course

    EMIA 2020. Since we noticed that students from different cultural background did not have enough opportunity to form bonds with each other. Thus, we made this all-in-one website to encourage cultural empathy and understanding among students. This website allows students to exchange information of their own culture, meanwhile appreciating others as well. We aim to create a more diverse and rapport enviroment in campus.

    Join us

    Unique Features

    Truly Top-Notch

    Using our website, you can self-organise events for the community. We have an AI culture assistant bot embedded as a pop-chat which can help you plan city hunt all over the world, so that you can explore a region with friends you met here. Also, our admin will share culture news about musics, languages, etc. in culture blogs section.
